{"type": "article", "id": 23868, "title": "极简车铃", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-15T07:00:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607123120N7Kf9wYxFo3p8LPj.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">澳大利亚品牌 Knog 专门做自行车配件，这个像戒指一样的圆环是自行车铃铛。它的特点就是小巧，只有 15 毫米宽，通过螺丝安装，改变了原本车铃笨重的感觉，几乎是隐藏的。在声音上，它能产生几个音调。有铝、黄铜、青铜、钛等 5 种材料和大小两种直径。产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/-oi/oi-the-bike-bell-that-doesnt-look-like-a-bike-bell?ref=project_link\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123114fP1UuRioGnzZEBj4.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.56259205\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123118nDEBYMcwfXI8WjdK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123118MyluTbmhX3U8sj1Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50441176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123118xkslqyXS1UArHeJi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.725\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123119SE9tWbsDiX1j2udC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123119GsCKBk5xfov08Jzq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}